      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUGATTI CANDY (8) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 5.5 lengths third (20.36) last time in a Maiden at Grafton over 350m. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Should be in this for a long way. CINNAMON SWIRL (5) shows ability but remains a maiden after 35 starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing fourth (20.42) at Grafton. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Has ability and can measure up. EDITH ACES (2) makes her debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Likely to run well.",
